(1729, NULL, 'import', '24963', 'IB Language B—World Language (Other Language)', 'IB Language B—World Language (Other Language) courses prepare students to take the International Baccalaureate Language B exams for a language not specified elsewhere in this classification system. These courses focus on improving students’ accuracy and fluency in oral and written communication (usually in the students’ “second” language).', 'Editorial Update', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, '2020-06-09 12:39:26', '2020-06-09 12:39:26'),
