(822, 'import', 'AZ06', 'Foreign Language and Literature', '153', 'IB Language A: Language and Literature—Spanish', 'IB Language A: Language and Literature—Spanish courses prepare students to take the International Baccalaureate Language A: Language and Literature exams at either the standard or higher level. Course content includes in-depth study of composition for purpose and audience, forms of mass communication and the media, and the context and elements of literature. The course includes oral and written assignments and is designed for students highly competent in using Spanish in an academic context.', '', NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '', '1', '0', '0', '1', '0', '42207', NULL, '1', '24067', '24', 'Foreign Language and Literature', '067', 'IB Language A: Language and Literature—Spanish', 'IB Language A: Language and Literature—Spanish courses prepare students to take the International Baccalaureate Language A: Language and Literature exams at either the standard or higher level. Course content includes in-depth study of composition for purpose and audience, forms of mass communication and the media, and the context and elements of literature. The course includes oral and written assignments and is designed for students highly competent in using Spanish in an academic context.', '1', '0', '0', '1', '0', 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:02', '2020-06-09 09:45:02'),
