(911, 'import', 'AZ08', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education', '051', 'Health Education', 'Topics covered within Health Education courses may vary widely, but typically include personal health (nutrition, mental health and stress management, drug/alcohol abuse prevention, disease prevention, and first aid) and consumer health issues. The courses may also include brief studies of environmental health, personal development, and/or community resources.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '08051', '08', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education', '051', 'Health Education', 'Topics covered within Health Education courses may vary widely, but typically include personal health (nutrition, mental health and stress management, drug/alcohol abuse prevention, disease prevention, and first aid) and consumer health issues. The courses may also include brief studies of environmental health, personal development, and/or community resources.', '0', '0', '0', '1', NULL, 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:02', '2020-06-09 09:45:02'),
(912, 'import', 'AZ08', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education', '052', 'Health and Fitness', 'Health and Fitness courses combine the topics of Health Education courses (nutrition, stress management, substance abuse prevention, disease prevention, first aid, and so on) with an active fitness component (typically including aerobic activity and fitness circuits) with the intention of conveying the importance of life-long wellness habits.', '', NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '08052', '08', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education', '052', 'Health and Fitness', 'Health and Fitness courses combine the topics of Health Education courses (nutrition, stress management, substance abuse prevention, disease prevention, first aid, and so on) with an active fitness component (typically including aerobic activity and fitness circuits) with the intention of conveying the importance of life-long wellness habits.', '0', '0', '0', '1', NULL, 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:02', '2020-06-09 09:45:02'),
(913, 'import', 'AZ08', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education', '053', 'Community Health', 'Community Health courses cover not only personal health topics (nutrition, stress management, substance abuse prevention, disease prevention, first aid, and so on), but also more general health issues. These additional topics may include (among others) available community resources, fundamentals of the nation’s health care system, contemporary world health issues, and career options within the health field.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '08053', '08', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education', '053', 'Community Health', 'Community Health courses cover not only personal health topics (nutrition, stress management, substance abuse prevention, disease prevention, first aid, and so on), but also more general health issues. These additional topics may include (among others) available community resources, fundamentals of the nation’s health care system, contemporary world health issues, and career options within the health field.', '0', '0', '0', '1', NULL, 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:02', '2020-06-09 09:45:02'),
(914, 'import', 'AZ08', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education', '054', 'Special Needs Health Education', 'Special Needs Health Education courses focus on the health requirements of individuals with special needs and emphasize meeting those needs within the home setting. These courses provide information regarding the elderly and individuals with disabilities, handicaps, and/or debilitating illnesses, along with strategies to prepare students for their possible roles as caretakers.', '', NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '08054', '08', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education', '054', 'Special Needs Health Education', '--This course was archived at the National level -- Special Needs Health Education courses focus on the health requirements of individuals with special needs and emphasize meeting those needs within the home setting. These courses provide information regarding the elderly and individuals with disabilities, handicaps, and/or debilitating illnesses, along with strategies to prepare students for their possible roles as caretakers.', '0', '0', '0', '1', NULL, 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:02', '2020-06-09 09:45:02'),
(915, 'import', 'AZ08', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education', '055', 'Safety and First Aid', 'Safety and First Aid courses provide specialized instruction in first aid techniques, cardiopulmonary resuscitation (CPR), relief of obstructed airways, and general safety procedures and behaviors. These courses may include such topics as an overview of community agencies and hotlines providing emergency care and information and opportunities for first aid and CPR certification.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '08055', '08', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education', '055', 'Safety and First Aid', 'Safety and First Aid courses provide specialized instruction in first aid techniques, cardiopulmonary resuscitation (CPR), relief of obstructed airways, and general safety procedures and behaviors. These courses may include such topics as an overview of community agencies and hotlines providing emergency care and information and opportunities for first aid and CPR certification.', '0', '0', '0', '1', NULL, 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:02', '2020-06-09 09:45:02'),
(916, 'import', 'AZ08', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education', '056', 'Health for Parenting Teens', 'Designed for pregnant teens and/or parents, topics within Health for Parenting Teens courses cover a wide range of both health and parenting issues, typically including prenatal and postnatal care, health and well-being of young parents, child development, stress management, and parental/adult roles. The courses may also involve academic assistance, career exploration, financial management, and so on.', '', NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '08056', '08', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education', '056', 'Health for Parenting Teens', 'Designed for pregnant teens and/or parents, topics within Health for Parenting Teens courses cover a wide range of both health and parenting issues, typically including prenatal and postnatal care, health and well-being of young parents, child development, stress management, and parental/adult roles. The courses may also involve academic assistance, career exploration, financial management, and so on.', '0', '0', '0', '1', NULL, 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:02', '2020-06-09 09:45:02'),
(917, 'import', 'AZ08', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education', '057', 'Health and Life Management', 'Health and Life Management courses focus as much on consumer education topics (such as money management and evaluation of consumer information and advertising) as on personal health topics (such as nutrition, stress management, drug/alcohol abuse prevention, disease prevention, and first aid). Course objectives include helping students develop decision-making, communication, interpersonal, and coping skills and strategies.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '08057', '08', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education', '057', 'Health and Life Management', 'Health and Life Management courses focus as much on consumer education topics (such as money management and evaluation of consumer information and advertising) as on personal health topics (such as nutrition, stress management, drug/alcohol abuse prevention, disease prevention, and first aid). Course objectives include helping students develop decision-making, communication, interpersonal, and coping skills and strategies.', '0', '0', '0', '1', NULL, 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:02', '2020-06-09 09:45:02'),
(918, 'import', 'AZ08', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education', '058', 'Substance Abuse Prevention', 'Substance Abuse Prevention courses focus specifically on the health risks of drugs, alcohol and tobacco. These courses provide information on the negative consequences of these products and teach students coping strategies to resist the influences (such as peers and media images) that may entice them to use these substances. Students may also explore the community resources available to them.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '08058', '08', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education', '058', 'Substance Abuse Prevention', 'Substance Abuse Prevention courses focus specifically on the health risks of drugs, alcohol and tobacco. These courses provide information on the negative consequences of these products and teach students coping strategies to resist the influences (such as peers and media images) that may entice them to use these substances. Students may also explore the community resources available to them.', '0', '0', '0', '1', NULL, 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:02', '2020-06-09 09:45:02'),
