(1418, 'import', 'AZ17', 'Architecture and Construction', '013', 'Commercial Construction', 'Commercial Construction courses focus on residential construction principles and their relationship to commercial applications. Topics typically covered include commercial concrete forming, reinforcement and placement methods, stair construction, metal framing, interior finishes, suspended ceiling systems, metal framing and drywall applications, and commercial roofing methods and systems. These courses may also address equipment and tool usage in commercial construction.', '', NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '41699', NULL, '1', '17013', '17', 'Architecture and Construction', '013', 'Commercial Construction', 'Commercial Construction courses focus on residential construction principles and their relationship to commercial applications. Topics typically covered include commercial concrete forming, reinforcement and placement methods, stair construction, metal framing, interior finishes, suspended ceiling systems, metal framing and drywall applications, and commercial roofing methods and systems. These courses may also address equipment and tool usage in commercial construction.', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:04', '2020-06-09 09:45:04'),
