(1773, 'import', 'AZ51', 'English Language and Literature (prior-to-secondary)', '203', 'English—Test Preparation', 'English—Test Preparation courses provide to students activities in analytical thinking and with the skills and strategies associated with standardized test taking. Topics covered include vocabulary, reading comprehension, and writing strategies, as well as time management, scoring procedures, and dealing with test-related stress. Course materials may include national and state standardized test review materials, current assessment software programs, and previous standardized examinations.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '51203', '51', 'English Language and Literature (prior-to-secondary)', '203', 'English—Test Preparation', 'English—Test Preparation courses provide to students activities in analytical thinking and with the skills and strategies associated with standardized test taking. Topics covered include vocabulary, reading comprehension, and writing strategies, as well as time management, scoring procedures, and dealing with test-related stress. Course materials may include national and state standardized test review materials, current assessment software programs, and previous standardized examinations.', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:05', '2020-06-09 09:45:05'),
