(1809, 'import', 'AZ52', 'Mathematics (prior-to-secondary)', '036', 'Mathematics (grade 6)', 'Mathematics (grade 6) courses typically emphasize skills in numerical operations (including basic operations and their proper order); measurement; patterns; simple functions; geometry; and concepts of data analysis, including statistics and probability. Specific content depends upon state standards for grade 6.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '52036', '52', 'Mathematics (prior-to-secondary)', '036', 'Mathematics (grade 6)', 'Mathematics (grade 6) courses typically emphasize skills in numerical operations (including basic operations and their proper order); measurement; patterns; simple functions; geometry; and concepts of data analysis, including statistics and probability. Specific content depends upon state standards for grade 6.', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:05', '2020-06-09 09:45:05'),
