(1991, 'import', 'AZ55', 'Fine and Performing Arts (prior-to-secondary)', '147', 'Music—Independent Study', 'Music—Independent Study courses, often conducted with instructors, professional musicians, or voice coaches as mentors, enable students to explore music-related topics. Independent Study courses may serve as an opportunity for students to expand their expertise in a particular form or style, to explore a topic in greater detail, or to develop more advanced skills.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '55147', '55', 'Fine and Performing Arts (prior-to-secondary)', '147', 'Music—Independent Study', 'Music—Independent Study courses, often conducted with instructors, professional musicians, or voice coaches as mentors, enable students to explore music-related topics. Independent Study courses may serve as an opportunity for students to expand their expertise in a particular form or style, to explore a topic in greater detail, or to develop more advanced skills.', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:06', '2020-06-09 09:45:06'),
