(2035, 'import', 'AZ56', 'Foreign Language and Literature (prior-to-secondary)', '039', 'Foreign Language', 'Code 56039, representing Foreign Language courses that are not grade differentiated, should be used when a state or locality does not have or does not employ grade-level content standards, when those standards may apply to a range of consecutive grades (e.g., “by 3rd grade, students should know and be able to do…”), or when the content descriptions above (Foreign Language, early childhood education through grade 8) do not fit the courses offered. The grade span element should be included to define which grades may be incorporated by this course code.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '56039', '56', 'Foreign Language and Literature (prior-to-secondary)', '039', 'Foreign Language', '--This course was archived at the National level -- Code 56039, representing Foreign Language courses that are not grade differentiated, should be used when a state or locality does not have or does not employ grade-level content standards, when those standards may apply to a range of consecutive grades (e.g., “by 3rd grade, students should know and be able to do…”), or when the content descriptions above (Foreign Language, early childhood education through grade 8) do not fit the courses offered. The grade span element should be included to define which grades may be incorporated by this course code.', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:06', '2020-06-09 09:45:06'),
