(2104, 'import', 'AZ58', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education  (prior-to-secondary)', '047', 'Physical Education—Independent Study', 'Courses in Physical Education—Independent Study, often conducted with instructors as mentors, enable students to explore topics of interest related to physical education. Independent Study courses may serve as an opportunity for students to expand their expertise in a particular sport or activity, to explore a topic in greater detail, or to develop more advanced skills.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '58047', '58', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education  (prior-to-secondary)', '047', 'Physical Education—Independent Study', 'Courses in Physical Education—Independent Study, often conducted with instructors as mentors, enable students to explore topics of interest related to physical education. Independent Study courses may serve as an opportunity for students to expand their expertise in a particular sport or activity, to explore a topic in greater detail, or to develop more advanced skills.', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:06', '2020-06-09 09:45:06'),
