(2106, 'import', 'AZ58', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education  (prior-to-secondary)', '051', 'Health Education', 'Topics covered within Health Education courses may vary widely, but typically include personal health (nutrition, mental health and stress management, drug/alcohol abuse prevention, disease prevention, and first aid) and consumer health issues. The courses may also include brief studies of environmental health, personal development, and/or community resources.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '58051', '58', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education  (prior-to-secondary)', '051', 'Health Education', 'Topics covered within Health Education courses may vary widely, but typically include personal health (nutrition, mental health and stress management, drug/alcohol abuse prevention, disease prevention, and first aid) and consumer health issues. The courses may also include brief studies of environmental health, personal development, and/or community resources.', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:06', '2020-06-09 09:45:06'),
(2107, 'import', 'AZ58', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education  (prior-to-secondary)', '052', 'Health and Fitness', 'Health and Fitness courses combine the topics of Health Education courses (nutrition, stress management, substance abuse prevention, disease prevention, first aid, and so on) with an active fitness component (typically including aerobic activity and fitness circuits) with the intention of conveying the importance of life-long wellness habits.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '58052', '58', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education  (prior-to-secondary)', '052', 'Health and Fitness', 'Health and Fitness courses combine the topics of Health Education courses (nutrition, stress management, substance abuse prevention, disease prevention, first aid, and so on) with an active fitness component (typically including aerobic activity and fitness circuits) with the intention of conveying the importance of life-long wellness habits.', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:06', '2020-06-09 09:45:06'),
(2108, 'import', 'AZ58', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education  (prior-to-secondary)', '057', 'Health and Life Management', 'Health and Life Management courses focus as much on consumer education topics (such as money management and evaluation of consumer information and advertising) as on personal health topics (such as nutrition, stress management, drug/alcohol abuse prevention, disease prevention, and first aid). Course objectives include helping students develop decisionmaking, communication, interpersonal, and coping skills and strategies.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '58057', '58', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education  (prior-to-secondary)', '057', 'Health and Life Management', 'Health and Life Management courses focus as much on consumer education topics (such as money management and evaluation of consumer information and advertising) as on personal health topics (such as nutrition, stress management, drug/alcohol abuse prevention, disease prevention, and first aid). Course objectives include helping students develop decisionmaking, communication, interpersonal, and coping skills and strategies.', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:07', '2020-06-09 09:45:07'),
(2109, 'import', 'AZ58', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education  (prior-to-secondary)', '058', 'Substance Abuse Prevention', 'Substance Abuse Prevention courses focus specifically on the health risks of drugs, alcohol, and tobacco. These courses provide information on the negative consequences of these products and teach students coping strategies to resist the influences (such as peers and media images) that may entice them to use these substances. Students may also explore the community resources available to them.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '58058', '58', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education  (prior-to-secondary)', '058', 'Substance Abuse Prevention', 'Substance Abuse Prevention courses focus specifically on the health risks of drugs, alcohol, and tobacco. These courses provide information on the negative consequences of these products and teach students coping strategies to resist the influences (such as peers and media images) that may entice them to use these substances. Students may also explore the community resources available to them.', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:07', '2020-06-09 09:45:07'),
(2110, 'import', 'AZ58', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education  (prior-to-secondary)', '097', 'Health Education—Independent Study', 'Courses in Health Education—Independent Study, often conducted with instructors as mentors, enable students to explore topics of interest related to health and health education. Independent Study courses may provide the opportunity for students to expand expertise in a particular application, to explore a topic of special interest in greater detail, or to develop more advanced skills.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '58097', '58', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education  (prior-to-secondary)', '097', 'Health Education—Independent Study', 'Courses in Health Education—Independent Study, often conducted with instructors as mentors, enable students to explore topics of interest related to health and health education. Independent Study courses may provide the opportunity for students to expand expertise in a particular application, to explore a topic of special interest in greater detail, or to develop more advanced skills.', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:07', '2020-06-09 09:45:07'),
(2111, 'import', 'AZ58', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education  (prior-to-secondary)', '997', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education—Independent Study', 'Courses in Physical, Health, and Safety Education—Independent Study, often conducted with instructors as mentors, enable students to explore topics of interest related to physical, health, and safety education. Independent Study courses may serve as an opportunity for students to expand their expertise in a particular application, to explore a topic in greater detail, or to develop more advanced physical, health, and/or safety skills.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '58997', '58', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education  (prior-to-secondary)', '997', 'Physical, Health, and Safety Education—Independent Study', 'Courses in Physical, Health, and Safety Education—Independent Study, often conducted with instructors as mentors, enable students to explore topics of interest related to physical, health, and safety education. Independent Study courses may serve as an opportunity for students to expand their expertise in a particular application, to explore a topic in greater detail, or to develop more advanced physical, health, and/or safety skills.', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:07', '2020-06-09 09:45:07'),
