(2148, 'import', 'AZ61', 'Communications and Audio/Visual Technology (prior-to-secondary)', '997', 'Communication and Audio/Video Technology—Independent Study', 'Communication and Audio/Video Technology—Independent Study courses, often conducted with instructors as mentors, enable students to explore topics of interest related to mass communication and its technologies. Independent Study courses may serve as an opportunity for students to expand their expertise in a particular application, to explore a topic in greater detail, or to develop more advanced skills.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '61997', '61', 'Communications and Audio/Visual Technology (prior-to-secondary)', '997', 'Communication and Audio/Video Technology—Independent Study', 'Communication and Audio/Video Technology—Independent Study courses, often conducted with instructors as mentors, enable students to explore topics of interest related to mass communication and its technologies. Independent Study courses may serve as an opportunity for students to expand their expertise in a particular application, to explore a topic in greater detail, or to develop more advanced skills.', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:07', '2020-06-09 09:45:07'),
