(2156, 'import', 'AZ62', 'Business and Marketing (prior-to-secondary)', '101', 'Banking and Finance', 'Banking and Finance courses provide an overview of the American monetary and banking system as well as types of financial institutions and the services and products that they offer. Course content may include government regulations; checking, savings, and money market accounts; loans; investments; and negotiable instruments.', '', NULL, NULL, '', '', '', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '40664', NULL, '1', '62101', '62', 'Business and Marketing (prior-to-secondary)', '101', 'Banking and Finance', 'Banking and Finance courses provide an overview of the American monetary and banking system as well as types of financial institutions and the services and products that they offer. Course content may include government regulations; checking, savings, and money market accounts; loans; investments; and negotiable instruments.', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:07', '2020-06-09 09:45:07'),
