(2233, 'import', 'AZ72', 'Academic Enrichment (prior-to-secondary)', '161', 'Montessori MS Service Learning/Internships/Class Business A', 'Students will be required to do a week long, half-day internship in a local business or organization. Each student will work extensively on career research and develop a resume before interning. Later in the year, students volunteer time on a local and/or national community service project. In economics, students run a class business, of their choice. Students keep records, prepare, track inventory, buy supplies, and sell the product.', '', NULL, NULL, '', NULL, '', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', '41550', NULL, '1', '72999', '72', 'Academic Enrichment (prior-to-secondary)', '999', 'Miscellaneous—Other', '', '0', '0', '1', '0', '0', 1, 1, '2020-06-09 09:45:07', '2020-06-09 09:45:07'),
